      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. i checked the app logs and they don't seem to show anything specific right before the reset happens. it feels super random though. could it be some kind of packet dropping or something happening at the network level that we just can't see? maybe something with the idle timeout on a load balancer if we're using one?",
